metadata.name: Origins #1
metadata.description: Our unique, location - based time lapses were each meticulously created by hand, one at a time.No algorithms.No artificial intelligence.Just one beautifully captured, never to be replicated moment in time, made up of 60 jaw dropping images of nature, and uniquely orchestrated music composed for each NFT.Discover levels of rarity based on the natural world inside and listen for the specialized music that signals greater distinction.  Visuals by Richard Mourant. Music by Jeremy Nathan Tisser.  Lyrics & Vocals by Ashley Tamar Davis.  Orchestra recorded live by FAMES Project, Macedonia. Conducted by Oleg Kondratenko. Orchestrations by Jeff Tinsley. Percussion arrangements by MB Gordy. Vocals recorded by Greg Karas at Karasene Studios in Los Angeles, CA. Music mixed by Michael Bouska. Assistants: Esin Aydingoz and Fadi Khoury.  Terms and conditions apply.Please review on our website.
